      "correct_choice_id": 2,
      "solution": "<div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>A) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=km0mfg&anker=Z3733d22ef7bb87f743207060acda0451\" data-learningcard-id=\"km0mfg\" data-anker=\"Z3733d22ef7bb87f743207060acda0451\" data-section-id=\"Pq1WA30\" data-sememe-id=\"8AbOlw\">Corticosteroids</a> are not commonly used in treatment for the <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Gs0Bwh&anker=Z828b1ca99b33821e1a4cd147fc26350a\" data-learningcard-id=\"Gs0Bwh\" data-anker=\"Z828b1ca99b33821e1a4cd147fc26350a\" data-sememe-id=\"FKWgRm0\">common colds</a>. <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=km0mfg&anker=Z7acc6b8a4fb3eecc9bdffe7ff1f88c25\" data-learningcard-id=\"km0mfg\" data-anker=\"Z7acc6b8a4fb3eecc9bdffe7ff1f88c25\" data-section-id=\"F8bgov\" data-sememe-id=\"YOanIk\">Prednisone</a> could potentially increase the infection risk.</div><div><h4 style='color: #34d399; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>B) CORRECT:</h4>Correct -- A <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Gs0Bwh&anker=Z828b1ca99b33821e1a4cd147fc26350a\" data-learningcard-id=\"Gs0Bwh\" data-anker=\"Z828b1ca99b33821e1a4cd147fc26350a\" data-sememe-id=\"FKWgRm0\">common cold</a> is a <span data-sememe-id=\"g4WFil0\">self-limited</span> viral infection requiring symptomatic treatment, including hydration, <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=xN0EWg&anker=Z937eb02dfdae5d3235cea8d72ffaf83f\" data-learningcard-id=\"xN0EWg\" data-anker=\"Z937eb02dfdae5d3235cea8d72ffaf83f\" data-section-id=\"5BXiY00\" data-sememe-id=\"CWbqns\">analgesics</a>, and decongestants such as <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=tN0X1g&anker=Ze33a778e294d4a55658e97b14940fddd\" data-learningcard-id=\"tN0X1g\" data-anker=\"Ze33a778e294d4a55658e97b14940fddd\" data-section-id=\"CIbqUE\" data-sememe-id=\"mNcVb10\">oxymetazoline</a>. Patients should be advised to return if symptoms worsen or if signs of secondary bacterial infection develop, such as <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=j50_Pg&anker=Za5de83449ff6a749e6c1348b93b1f3b1\" data-learningcard-id=\"j50_Pg\" data-anker=\"Za5de83449ff6a749e6c1348b93b1f3b1\" data-sememe-id=\"CL0q-g\">fever</a>, <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=qh0CUf&anker=Zfdfb82d83e675513c49619bc646fd20c\" data-learningcard-id=\"qh0CUf\" data-anker=\"Zfdfb82d83e675513c49619bc646fd20c\" data-section-id=\"PFcWRV0\" data-sememe-id=\"vIYAeq\">purulent</a> discharge, or respiratory symptoms.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>C) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=mm0VTg&anker=Z9884c173cd8bcd36d44eb85ea8acfec2\" data-learningcard-id=\"mm0VTg\" data-anker=\"Z9884c173cd8bcd36d44eb85ea8acfec2\" data-section-id=\"Sjcy-X0\" data-sememe-id=\"nOa7Gk\">Azithromycin</a> is not indicated for viral <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=tF0XP3&anker=Z20ffbe5edb7667e7ff0930a27b0d0d14\" data-learningcard-id=\"tF0XP3\" data-anker=\"Z20ffbe5edb7667e7ff0930a27b0d0d14\" data-sememe-id=\"1vb2_v\">upper respiratory infections</a>. <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=mm0VTg&anker=Z4660f53b2b0c85aa3f9ab01bdf3f14f3\" data-learningcard-id=\"mm0VTg\" data-anker=\"Z4660f53b2b0c85aa3f9ab01bdf3f14f3\">Antibiotics</a> should only be considered if secondary bacterial infection develops, which typically manifests with worsening symptoms after initial improvement.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>D) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=S80yN3&anker=Z2b7edf3ee0203011545786467a61cbd8\" data-learningcard-id=\"S80yN3\" data-anker=\"Z2b7edf3ee0203011545786467a61cbd8\" data-sememe-id=\"SeXyyC\">Chest radiograph</a> is not routinely recommended for diagnosing a <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Gs0Bwh&anker=Z828b1ca99b33821e1a4cd147fc26350a\" data-learningcard-id=\"Gs0Bwh\" data-anker=\"Z828b1ca99b33821e1a4cd147fc26350a\" data-sememe-id=\"FKWgRm0\">common cold</a>. Imaging is only indicated if <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=mh0Vef&anker=Z36f83311c3582932defdae7a73e5730b\" data-learningcard-id=\"mh0Vef\" data-anker=\"Z36f83311c3582932defdae7a73e5730b\" data-sememe-id=\"rk0f6T\">pneumonia</a> due to secondary bacterial infection is suspected, which is not suggested by this patient's stable symptoms and clear <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=tl0XAT&anker=Zd570ad70c7fd2207a7ad9e4d0c4279c5\" data-learningcard-id=\"tl0XAT\" data-anker=\"Zd570ad70c7fd2207a7ad9e4d0c4279c5\">lung examination</a>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>E) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=mm0VTg&anker=Z4660f53b2b0c85aa3f9ab01bdf3f14f3\" data-learningcard-id=\"mm0VTg\" data-anker=\"Z4660f53b2b0c85aa3f9ab01bdf3f14f3\">Antibiotics</a> are not indicated for a <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Gs0Bwh&anker=Z828b1ca99b33821e1a4cd147fc26350a\" data-learningcard-id=\"Gs0Bwh\" data-anker=\"Z828b1ca99b33821e1a4cd147fc26350a\" data-sememe-id=\"FKWgRm0\">common cold</a> because it is a viral infection. <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=mm0VTg&anker=Ze97a66c8da9aeb9b6f20243b4f8a11ff\" data-learningcard-id=\"mm0VTg\" data-anker=\"Ze97a66c8da9aeb9b6f20243b4f8a11ff\" data-section-id=\"jRc_5X0\" data-sememe-id=\"ROalHk\">Amoxicillin</a> is inappropriate, unless secondary bacterial infection is suspected.</div>",
